name: Non Fungible Cards collection 09 - Don't Forget: There are plenty of tokens outside
description: This is a reminder for you. There are lots of tokens outside waiting to be captured. They may be a photograph, a drawing, a poetry, a song or whatever creative trick you can do. Nature delivers tokens by the bunch and it's only up to you to capture them. This card is cheap, so you can gift a friend or a family member, or simply have it in your digital wallet to inspire you.
